data.title: Utah Jazz Roster
data.meta_description: Utah Jazz scores, news, schedule, players, stats, rumors, depth charts and more on RealGM.com
data.text:
Andrei Kirilenko was selected as the #24 pick in the First Round of the 1999 NBA Draft by the Utah Jazz. Andrei Kirilenko signed a multi-year contract with the Utah Jazz on August 16, 2001. Andrei Kirilenko signed a multi-year extension with the Utah Jazz on October 29, 2004.

Kosta Koufos was selected as the #23 pick in the First Round of the 2008 NBA Draft by the Utah Jazz. Kosta Koufos signed a multi-year contract with the Utah Jazz on July 10, 2008.

C.J. Miles was selected as the #4 pick in the Second Round of the 2005 NBA Draft by the Utah Jazz. C.J. Miles signed a multi-year contract with the Utah Jazz on July 11, 2005. C.J. Miles re-signed to a contract as a free agent with the Utah Jazz on October 1, 2007. C.J. Miles re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Utah Jazz on July 29, 2008.

Paul Millsap was selected as the #17 pick in the Second Round of the 2006 NBA Draft by the Utah Jazz. Paul Millsap signed a multi-year contract with the Utah Jazz on August 1, 2006. Paul Millsap re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Utah Jazz on July 20, 2009.

Deron Williams was selected as the #3 pick in the First Round of the 2005 NBA Draft by the Utah Jazz. Deron Williams signed a multi-year contract with the Utah Jazz on July 11, 2005. Deron Williams signed a multi-year extension with the Utah Jazz on July 18, 2008.

Carlos Boozer signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Utah Jazz on July 30, 2004.

Sundiata Gaines signed a contract with the Utah Jazz on January 5, 2010. Sundiata Gaines re-signed to a contract as a free agent with the Utah Jazz on January 15, 2010. Sundiata Gaines re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Utah Jazz on January 25, 2010.

Othyus Jeffers signed a contract with the Utah Jazz on March 4, 2010. Othyus Jeffers re-signed to a contract as a free agent with the Utah Jazz on March 14, 2010. Othyus Jeffers re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Utah Jazz on March 24, 2010.

Wesley Matthews signed a contract as a free agent with the Utah Jazz on September 21, 2009.

Mehmet Okur signed a multi-year contract with the Utah Jazz on July 27, 2004. Mehmet Okur re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Utah Jazz on July 8, 2009.

Ronnie Price signed a multi-year contract with the Utah Jazz on July 26, 2007. Ronnie Price re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Utah Jazz on July 14, 2009.
